  "cascade": {
    "method": "Cascade NOT effective for Q4 (sem_map / image color extraction). dase 6-color anchor classification on image-caption embeddings: only 10/294 (3%) confident at TAU_HIGH=0.05; the remaining 284 must go to BQ. Cost saving 1.04\u00d7 \u2193, ARI -0.002 (negligible). Cascade essentially equals baseline. Reporting cascade = baseline",
    "_finding_note": "Paper Table 4 reports DASE+NN as X (not applicable) for Q4 because 'embedding-based prefiltering is less accurate for semantic merge (M) tasks' (paper \u00a75.1). Image-caption embeddings encode many product attributes (style, material, etc.) weighting color only weakly \u2014 anchor-based color classification has top1-top2 margins typically < 0.05. Cluster-based and threshold-based cascades cannot preserve quality AND save cost on image-color sem_map",
